The one thing that I have learnt from the ups and downs of my life is that positivity has to be a choice that we make every day. This is true especially when we are at our lowest. A positive mindset and attitude can lead us halfway through a battle to victory. Never give in to negative thoughts or people’s perceptions of yourself. Keep doing what you need to do, give it your best, and have faith in what is to unfold & yourself. Even if it doesn’t go your way temporarily, you will see things shaping up in unexpected ways in the future; because in life... EVERYTHING HAPPENS FOR THE BEST 🤗🌈✨
